casebody.data:
Thursday, March 19, 1998

MOTION DOCKET

96-2641. In re Hitchcock.

Cuyahoga App. Nos. 69291 and 69292. This cause came on for further consideration upon appellant’s motion for emergency stay of proceedings. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for emergency stay of proceedings be, and hereby is, denied.

Resnick J., dissents.
